      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SAPPHIRE LEXI (1) is a first starter from the Michelle Popowski kennel by Barcia Bale out of Treasure Tears. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Expected to be well fancied and can make an immediate impact. ZIPPING GOOFY (3) well back settling but did wind up strongly to finish 4th and beaten only 1.5 lengths (16.28) at The Gardens. Has placed several times at this track. Expected to feature in the finish. CLYDE'S REVENGE (2) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 388m behind Bigbad Esme (23.68) in a Maiden. Can measure up this time. SECRET BULLET (7) will be hard to beat despite making her debut at this circuit.",
